<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Red Hat Satellite 6.17 Complete Demo Report</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee0000 0%, #cc0000 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,');
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            position: relative;
        }

        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
            position: relative;
        }

        .phases-section {
            padding: 50px;
            background: white;
        }

        .phases-title {
            color: #ee0000;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #ee0000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .phase-timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .timeline-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #28a745, #20c997);
        }

        .phase-item {
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
        }

        .phase-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -65px;
            top: 30px;
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            background: #28a745;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(40,167,69,0.3);
        }

        .phase-number {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .phase-title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .phase-description {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .achievements-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .achievement-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .achievement-number {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .achievement-label {
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stats-overview {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #343a40 0%, #495057 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        .stats-title {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stat-description {
            font-size: 1em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .compliance-section {
            padding: 50px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .compliance-title {
            color: #ee0000;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .compliance-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .compliance-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 6px solid #28a745;
        }

        .compliance-card.insights {
            border-top-color: #17a2b8;
        }

        .compliance-card.rhc {
            border-top-color: #fd7e14;
        }

        .compliance-card h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.6em;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }

        .feature-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: #17a2b8;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 15px;
            }
            
            .phases-section, .stats-overview, .compliance-section {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .phase-timeline {
                padding-left: 40px;
            }
            
            .achievements-grid, .stats-grid, .compliance-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1> Red Hat Satellite 6.17</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Complete Management Demo - Ansible Automation Platform 2.5</p>
        </div>

        <div class="phases-section">
            <h2 class="phases-title"> Implementation Phases</h2>
            
            <div class="phase-timeline">
                <div class="timeline-line"></div>
                
                <div class="phase-item">
                    <div class="phase-number">1</div>
                    <h3 class="phase-title"> Repository Management</h3>
                    <p class="phase-description">
                        Complete setup of Red Hat repositories including RHEL 9 BaseOS, AppStream, 
                        Supplementary packages, and Satellite 6.17 repositories with automated sync plans.
                    </p>
                    <div class="achievements-grid">
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.repositories_enabled }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Repositories Enabled</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">2</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Sync Plans Created</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="phase-item">
                    <div class="phase-number">2</div>
                    <h3 class="phase-title"> Content Lifecycle Management</h3>
                    <p class="phase-description">
                        Establishment of DEV/TEST/PROD lifecycle environments, content views with 
                        dependency solving, composite content views, and activation key generation.
                    </p>
                    <div class="achievements-grid">
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.lifecycle_environments_created }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Lifecycle Environments</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.content_views_created }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Content Views</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.activation_keys_created }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Activation Keys</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.host_collections_created }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Host Collections</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="phase-item">
                    <div class="phase-number">3</div>
                    <h3 class="phase-title"> Host Management Operations</h3>
                    <p class="phase-description">
                        Comprehensive host registration, package update management including CVE patches,
                        security updates, bugfix updates, and Red Hat Insights/RHC integration.
                    </p>
                    <div class="achievements-grid">
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.update_operations_performed }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Update Operations</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="achievement-box">
                            <div class="achievement-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.compliance_integrations }}</div>
                            <div class="achievement-label">Compliance Integrations</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-overview">
            <h2 class="stats-title"> Demo Statistics</h2>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">1</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Satellite Organization</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.repositories_enabled }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Repositories Managed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.lifecycle_environments_created }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Lifecycle Environments</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.content_views_created }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Content Views</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.activation_keys_created }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Activation Keys</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon"></div>
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ demo_summary.operation_counts.update_operations_performed }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-description">Update Operations</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="compliance-section">
            <h2 class="compliance-title"> Enterprise Compliance & Integration</h2>
            <div class="compliance-grid">
                <div class="compliance-card insights">
                    <h3> Red Hat Insights Integration</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Automated client installation and registration</li>
                        <li>Continuous system health monitoring</li>
                        <li>Proactive vulnerability identification</li>
                        <li>Performance optimization recommendations</li>
                        <li>Compliance drift detection</li>
                        <li>Automated remediation suggestions</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="compliance-card rhc">
                    <h3> Red Hat Connector (RHC)</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Secure cloud-to-premise connectivity</li>
                        <li>Remote system management capabilities</li>
                        <li>Unified hybrid cloud operations</li>
                        <li>Automated patch management</li>
                        <li>Real-time system monitoring</li>
                        <li>Enterprise security integration</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="compliance-card">
                    <h3> Security & CVE Management</h3>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Targeted CVE patch deployment</li>
                        <li>Automated security update scheduling</li>
                        <li>Critical vulnerability remediation</li>
                        <li>System hardening maintenance</li>
                        <li>Compliance baseline enforcement</li>
                        <li>Enterprise audit trail</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3> Demo Complete!</h3>
            <p>Red Hat Satellite 6.17 comprehensive management automation successfully demonstrated</p>
            <p><strong>Generated:</strong> {{ demo_summary.timestamp }} | <strong>Server:</strong> {{ demo_summary.satellite_server }}</p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="https://access.redhat.com/products/red-hat-satellite">Red Hat Satellite</a>
                <a href="https://access.redhat.com/products/red-hat-insights">Red Hat Insights</a>
                <a href="https://www.redhat.com/en/technologies/management/ansible">Ansible Automation Platform</a>
                <a href="https://console.redhat.com/insights">Red Hat Console</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
